** sch_path: /foss/designs/chipathon-2026-gf180mcu-hall-effect-sensor/xschem/chopper/b9_chopper_tb_basic.sch
**.subckt b9_chopper_tb_basic
x1 vdd phi1 vss vin_p phi2 vin_n vout_p vout_n b9_chopper
